File		: ChatLine.mxml
Module		: Video Editing
Developer(s): Vimal Mahendran, Sreelekshmi, Ashish Pillai
Reviewer(s)	: Remya T

File used for creating a line between each chat conversation in Video Editing chat block.

-->

<mx:UIComponent xmlns:mx="http://www.adobe.com/2006/mxml">
	<mx:Script>
		<![CDATA[
			/**
			 * @public
			 * Function for drawing a line by passing the co ordinates.
			 *
			 * @param x of type Number
			 * @param y of type Number
			 * @param l of type Number
		 * @return void
			  */
			public function init(x:Number, y:Number, l:Number):void
			{
				graphics.lineStyle(1, 1, 1);
				graphics.beginFill(0x000000);
				graphics.moveTo(x, y - l);
				graphics.lineTo(x, y + l);
			}
		]]>
	</mx:Script>

</mx:UIComponent>
